locality: Reserve Naturelle Marojejy, along the trail to the summit of Marojejy Est, below the third camp; lichen forest and exposed wind-swept ridges. Collected with: A. Rakotozafy, G.E. Schatz, F. Badré & J. Randrianasolo.
